/* General page */
"管理系统权限、启动行为、界面外观和其他通用设置。" = "Manage permissions, launch behavior, appearance, and other general settings.";
"辅助功能权限" = "Accessibility Permission";
"授权后可自动回到原应用并粘贴，也可使用按住右键滑出和附加手势；未授权时仍可复制后手动粘贴。" = "With permission, Edge Clip can return to the previous app and paste automatically, and can also use right-button slide-out and auxiliary gestures. Without permission, it still copies the content so you can paste manually.";
"已授权" = "Granted";
"未授权" = "Not Granted";
"已授权后，选择记录会自动回到原应用并粘贴，也可以使用按住右键滑出和附加手势。" = "Once granted, selecting an item returns to the previous app and pastes automatically. Right-button slide-out and auxiliary gestures are also available.";
"未授权时，会先复制内容并回到原应用，由你手动粘贴；按住右键滑出和附加手势也不可用。" = "Without permission, Edge Clip copies the content and returns to the previous app so you can paste manually. Right-button slide-out and auxiliary gestures are unavailable.";
"刷新状态" = "Refresh";
"立即授权" = "Grant Now";
