"Edge Clip 会跟随系统自动启动。" = "Edge Clip will launch automatically when your Mac starts.";
"系统重启后需要手动启动 Edge Clip。" = "You'll need to launch Edge Clip manually after restart.";
"界面外观" = "Appearance";
"设置窗口和剪贴面板的显示风格。" = "Adjust how the settings window and clipboard panel look.";
"应用可见性" = "App Visibility";
"菜单栏图标和程序坞显示方式会统一放在这里管理。" = "Manage the menu bar icon and Dock visibility here.";
"菜单栏图标" = "Menu Bar Icon";
"关闭后不会在菜单栏显示图标、右键菜单和最新一条内容摘要。" = "When turned off, the menu bar icon, right-click menu, and latest item preview are hidden.";
"程序坞图标" = "Dock Icon";
"关闭后只会在设置面板打开时暂时显示，关闭设置面板后会从程序坞隐藏。" = "When turned off, the Dock icon appears only while Settings is open and hides again afterward.";

/* Interaction page */
"请至少保留一种唤出方式，否则无法快速打开剪贴面板。" = "Keep at least one way to open the panel, or you won't be able to access it quickly.";
"选择一种顺手的唤出方式，再按需要调整触发条件。" = "Choose the way that feels most natural, then tune the trigger details as needed.";
"边缘唤出" = "Edge Trigger";
"鼠标移到所选屏幕边缘即可打开面板，适合单手操作。" = "Move the pointer to the selected screen edge to open the panel. Great for one-handed use.";
"选择边缘" = "Edge";
"决定边缘唤出监听屏幕左侧还是右侧。默认使用屏幕右侧。" = "Choose whether edge trigger listens on the left or right side of the screen. The default is the right edge.";
"出现位置" = "Panel Position";
"边缘激活位置" = "Edge Trigger Position";
"拖动蓝条调整面板出现高度。所选边缘会同步显示实际激活区域，松手后生效。" = "Drag the blue bar to adjust the panel's vertical position. The selected edge previews the active area live, and the change applies when you release.";
"靠下" = "Lower";
"靠上" = "Upper";
"当前靠上" = "Currently Near the Top";
"当前居中" = "Currently Centered";
"当前靠下" = "Currently Near the Bottom";
"边缘触发阈值" = "Edge Trigger Threshold";
"控制鼠标要多贴近所选边缘，才开始等待展开。数值越大越容易触发，数值越小越不容易误碰。" = "Controls how close the pointer must be to the selected edge before Edge Clip starts waiting to open. Higher values trigger more easily; lower values reduce accidental activation.";
"边缘触发延迟" = "Edge Trigger Delay";
"控制鼠标进入所选边缘热区后，要停留多久才展开面板。" = "Controls how long the pointer must remain in the selected hot edge before the panel opens.";
"已设为 0 ms：响应最快，也更容易误触发。" = "Set to 0 ms: fastest response, but also easier to trigger by accident.";
"鼠标离开面板的收起距离" = "Auto-Collapse Distance";
"控制鼠标离开面板多远后才自动收起面板。数值越大越不容易误收起，数值越小则收起更干脆但不易点击到位于边缘的按钮。" = "Controls how far the pointer can move away from the panel before it collapses automatically. Higher values reduce accidental collapse; lower values collapse faster but make edge buttons harder to reach.";
"已设为 0 px：鼠标一离开面板，就会更快自动收回。" = "Set to 0 px: the panel retracts as soon as the pointer leaves it.";
"快捷键唤出" = "Hotkey Trigger";
"可设置按键方式，以及快捷键唤出时的面板位置。" = "Choose the trigger style and where the panel appears when opened by hotkey.";
"面板位置" = "Panel Placement";
"按键方式" = "Trigger Style";
"双击修饰键适合只用修饰键唤出；组合按键可录入完整快捷键。" = "Double modifier works well if you want to trigger with modifiers only. Key combination lets you record a full shortcut.";
"双击修饰键打开剪贴面板" = "Open Clipboard Panel with Double Modifier";
"双击修饰键打开收藏标签" = "Open Favorites Tab with Double Modifier";
"可能与中英切换冲突。" = "May conflict with keyboard language switching.";
"不启用" = "Disabled";
"组合按键打开剪贴面板" = "Open Clipboard Panel with Key Combination";
"组合按键打开收藏标签" = "Open Favorites Tab with Key Combination";
"请录入快捷键" = "Press a Shortcut";
"组合按键至少需要一个修饰键。" = "A key combination must include at least one modifier.";
"组合按键不能重复；请为两个动作录入不同快捷键。" = "The key combinations can't be the same. Please record different shortcuts for the two actions.";
"双击修饰键不能重复；请为收藏标签选择其他修饰键。" = "The double modifier can't be reused. Please choose another modifier for Favorites.";
"菜单栏唤出" = "Menu Bar Trigger";
"打开后，点击菜单栏图标可以显示面板。" = "When enabled, clicking the menu bar icon opens the panel.";
"菜单栏显示最新一条内容" = "Show Latest Item in Menu Bar";
"打开后，会在图标右侧显示最新一条记录；关闭后只保留图标。" = "When enabled, the latest item appears beside the icon. When disabled, only the icon remains.";
"按住右键滑出" = "Right-Button Slide-Out";
"按住右键向右拖动即可打开面板，继续上下移动可切换记录，松手即可粘贴；启用前需要辅助功能权限。" = "Hold the right mouse button and drag right to open the panel. Move up or down to switch items, then release to paste. Accessibility permission is required.";
"横向触发距离" = "Horizontal Trigger Distance";
"控制按住右键后，向右拖多远才展开面板。" = "Controls how far you must drag right while holding the right mouse button before the panel opens.";
"会占用右键拖动操作" = "Uses Right-Drag Actions";
"开启后会接管按住右键后的拖动操作，可能与 BetterTouchTool 等手势软件冲突。只保留少量常用动作时，可以直接在下方配置附加手势。" = "When enabled, Edge Clip takes over right-button drag actions, which may conflict with gesture tools such as BetterTouchTool. If you only need a few common actions, configure auxiliary gestures below instead.";
"附加手势" = "Auxiliary Gestures";
"附加手势列表" = "Auxiliary Gesture List";
"添加手势" = "Add Gesture";
"暂无附加手势。点击“添加手势”创建第一条规则。" = "No auxiliary gestures yet. Click “Add Gesture” to create your first rule.";
"这将同时关闭菜单栏唤出剪贴面板的功能。" = "This also turns off opening the clipboard panel from the menu bar.";
"下次请从菜单栏或者访达的应用程序入口打开设置面板" = "Next time, open Settings from the menu bar or from the Applications entry in Finder.";
"下次请从访达的应用程序入口打开设置面板" = "Next time, open Settings from the Applications entry in Finder.";
"这将同时开启菜单栏图标。" = "This also turns on the menu bar icon.";
"连续预览会占用更多性能，遇到大文件或大量历史记录时建议按需开启。" = "Continuous preview uses more resources. Turn it on only when needed if you're working with large files or lots of history.";
"按住右键滑出需要辅助功能权限，正在为你发起系统授权申请。" = "Right-button slide-out requires Accessibility permission. Edge Clip is opening the system permission prompt now.";

/* Preferences page */
"调整粘贴方式、历史清理规则和完整预览方式。" = "Adjust how items are pasted, how history is cleaned up, and how full preview behaves.";
"粘贴方式" = "Paste Behavior";
"决定选中记录后如何回到原应用，以及已使用记录是否自动置顶。" = "Choose how Edge Clip returns to the previous app after selection, and whether used items move to the top automatically.";
"自动粘贴（需要辅助功能权限）" = "Auto Paste (Requires Accessibility Permission)";
"粘贴后记录位置" = "Position After Paste";
"可选择保持原位置，或在粘贴后将该条记录自动置顶。" = "Keep the item where it is, or automatically move it to the top after pasting.";
"数据存储" = "Storage";
"统一管理存储位置、记录数量、保存时长和磁盘占用。" = "Manage the storage location, history size, retention period, and disk usage in one place.";
"存储位置" = "Storage Location";
"修改…" = "Change…";
"在访达中显示" = "Show in Finder";
"恢复默认" = "Restore Default";
"正在迁移数据…" = "Migrating data…";
"占用磁盘空间上限" = "Disk Usage Limit";
"最大历史记录条数" = "Maximum History Items";
"超过后自动清理最旧且未收藏的记录" = "When exceeded, the oldest non-favorite items are removed automatically.";
"存储时间限制" = "Retention Period";
"完整预览" = "Full Preview";
"控制按空格查看内容的方式。中大文本默认只显示部分内容，不会展开全文。" = "Control how content opens with the Space key. Medium and large texts show only a partial preview by default instead of expanding the entire text.";
"按空格预览" = "Preview with Space";
"按空格查看当前记录的预览内容；中大文本只会显示部分内容。" = "Press Space to preview the current item. Medium and large texts show only part of the content.";
"连续预览" = "Continuous Preview";
"打开完整预览后，停留在其他可预览记录上会继续切换。" = "After opening full preview, moving over other previewable items continues switching the preview.";

/* Panel page */
"把常用标签放到前面，也可以在这里了解连续粘贴怎么用。" = "Move your most-used tabs to the front, and learn how continuous paste works here too.";
"顶部标签" = "Top Tabs";
"根据使用习惯个性化调整剪贴面板上的标签。" = "Customize the tabs shown in the clipboard panel to match your workflow.";
"标签切换方式" = "Tab Switching";
"默认鼠标悬停到标签上就会切换，也可以改成点击标签后再切换。" = "By default, hovering a tab switches to it. You can change that to click-to-switch instead.";
"“按住右键滑出”的交互方式仅支持鼠标悬停切换标签。" = "The right-button slide-out interaction supports hover-based tab switching only.";
"堆栈（连续粘贴）" = "Stack (Continuous Paste)";
"把多条文字先放进待贴清单里，再按顺序一条条使用，适合填表、批量录入和重复操作。" = "Put multiple text items into a pending list, then use them one by one in order. Great for forms, batch entry, and repetitive tasks.";
"常显时空闲透明度" = "Idle Transparency While Pinned";
"仅在开启面板常显后，鼠标移出面板并点击外部时生效；回到面板内或打开子面板时会恢复不透明。" = "Only applies when the panel is pinned open and you click outside after moving the pointer away. Opacity returns to normal when you move back into the panel or open a subpanel.";
"透明度" = "Transparency";
"0% 表示保持不透明，相当于关闭空闲降透明；90% 表示非常透明，不提供完全透明。" = "0% keeps the panel opaque, which is the same as disabling idle transparency. 90% is very transparent. Fully transparent is not supported.";
"已设为 0%：开启面板常显后，点击外部也会保持不透明。" = "Set to 0%: the panel stays opaque even after you pin it open and click outside.";
"当前透明度较高：面板会更不挡视线，但列表内容可读性也会明显下降。" = "The current transparency is quite high. The panel blocks less of the screen, but list readability also drops noticeably.";
"按住蓝色标签可拖动排序" = "Drag blue tabs to reorder them";
"按住末尾的灰色标签并拖动到蓝色标签区域可替换" = "Drag a gray tab from the end into the blue tab area to replace it";
"“全部”和“收藏”不可被替换和移动位置" = "“All” and “Favorites” cannot be replaced or moved";
"查看每个标签会显示什么" = "See what each tab shows";
"查看所有历史记录。" = "See all history items.";
"只看你标记为收藏的内容。" = "See only items you've marked as favorites.";
"句子、段落、聊天内容等普通文字。" = "Sentences, paragraphs, chat messages, and other plain text.";
"像代码的内容会集中放在这里，找起来更快。" = "Code-like content is grouped here so it's easier to find.";
"复制的链接或网页地址会出现在这里。" = "Copied links and webpage URLs appear here.";
"详细了解堆栈（连续粘贴）功能如何使用" = "Learn how Stack (Continuous Paste) works";
"先找到入口" = "Find the Entry Point";
"把内容放进去" = "Put Content Into It";
"按你的顺序整理" = "Arrange It Your Way";
"想贴哪条就用哪条" = "Use Exactly the Item You Want";
"也可以顺着一直贴下去" = "You Can Also Paste Straight Through";
"想直接用复制和粘贴快捷键连续操作？" = "Want to keep working with copy and paste shortcuts?";
"如果你想直接用 Command + C 和 Command + V 连续收集和粘贴，请先在“通用”里打开辅助功能权限。未开启时，堆栈仍然可以手动整理、查看和继续使用。" = "If you want to collect and paste continuously with Command + C and Command + V, first enable Accessibility permission in General. Without it, the stack can still be arranged, viewed, and reused manually.";
"从剪贴面板打开" = "Open from the Clipboard Panel";
"从完整预览开始" = "Start from Full Preview";
"右上角这个按钮就是堆栈入口。" = "This button in the top-right corner opens the stack.";
"这里会把当前文本带进堆栈。" = "This brings the current text into the stack.";
"截图、照片和其他图片内容。" = "Screenshots, photos, and other image content.";
"文档、附件、文件夹等项目。" = "Documents, attachments, folders, and similar items.";
"打开剪贴面板后，点击右上角高亮的堆叠图标就会进入堆栈。按空格查看完整预览时，右上角也有同样的入口。" = "After opening the clipboard panel, click the highlighted stack icon in the top-right to enter the stack. The same entry also appears in the top-right when you open full preview with Space.";
"进入后，在其他应用里继续复制文字，新的内容会加入待贴清单。查看可完整预览的文本时，也可以直接把当前内容带进堆栈。想把一整段内容拆成多条时，也可以点右上角的“数据处理”来整理。" = "Once you're in, keep copying text in other apps and new content will be added to the pending list. When viewing text that supports full preview, you can also bring the current content directly into the stack. If you want to split a long block into multiple items, use \"Data Processing\" in the top-right.";
"可以拖动调整顺序，也可以删掉暂时不用的内容。最上面会标出“下一条”，方便你一眼看清接下来会先用哪一项。" = "You can drag to reorder items or remove ones you do not need for now. The top item is marked as \"Next\" so you can instantly see what will be used first.";
"每一条左侧都有插入按钮。点哪一条，就会把哪一条直接送回当前输入框；用掉之后，下面的内容会自动补上来。" = "Each item has an insert button on the left. Click one to send it straight back to the current input field, and the next items move up automatically after it is used.";
"如果你更习惯键盘，回到目标位置后继续按 Command + V，Edge Clip 会按当前顺序一条条送出内容，适合连续填写多项信息。" = "If you prefer the keyboard, return to the target field and keep pressing Command + V. Edge Clip will send items one by one in the current order, which works well for filling multiple fields continuously.";

