/* About and credits */
"数据与隐私" = "Data & Privacy";
"边缘唤出的 macOS 剪贴板工具" = "A macOS clipboard tool that slides out from the edge";
"把最近复制过的文本、图片和文件收进一个随手可开的侧边面板里，方便继续查找、预览和回贴。" = "Keep recently copied text, images, and files in an easy-to-open side panel so you can keep searching, previewing, and pasting.";
"访问官网" = "Visit Website";
"查看欢迎引导" = "View Onboarding";
"偏好设置…" = "Preferences…";
"退出 Edge Clip" = "Quit Edge Clip";
"日常使用" = "Daily Use";
"从打开、定位到回贴，尽量减少打断和重复操作。" = "From opening to locating to pasting back, Edge Clip tries to reduce interruptions and repeated work.";
"就近打开面板" = "Open the Panel Nearby";
"支持边缘唤出、快捷键、菜单栏和右键滑出几种方式，方便在不同使用习惯下快速唤出。" = "Use edge trigger, hotkeys, the menu bar, or right-button slide-out to open the panel quickly in different workflows.";
"快速定位内容" = "Find Content Quickly";
"统一整理文本、图片和文件历史，支持分类筛选、关键词搜索和收藏。" = "Keep text, image, and file history together, with category filters, keyword search, and favorites.";
"预览后再决定" = "Preview Before You Decide";
"可以先查看内容，再决定是否回贴、收藏，或继续整理成堆栈。" = "Preview first, then decide whether to paste back, favorite it, or organize it into the stack.";
"连续回贴更顺手" = "Continuous Paste Feels Better";
"支持 1-9 快捷编号和剪贴板堆栈，适合批量录入、表单填写和重复操作。" = "Supports 1-9 quick slots and the clipboard stack, which is great for batch entry, forms, and repetitive work.";
"默认本地保存，按需授权，并明确说明默认敏感应用保护与可能的网络访问。" = "Stored locally by default, authorized only when needed, with clear explanations for default sensitive-app protection and possible network access.";
"查看详细的数据与隐私声明" = "View Full Data & Privacy Statement";
"历史记录保存在本机" = "History Stays on This Mac";
"文本、图片和文件历史默认只保存在这台 Mac 上，不依赖账号体系或云端同步。" = "Text, image, and file history is stored on this Mac by default, without accounts or cloud sync.";
"权限按需开启" = "Permissions Only When Needed";
"只有全局唤出、自动粘贴和部分快捷操作需要额外系统授权，未授权时仍可正常记录基础历史。" = "Only global triggers, auto paste, and some shortcuts need extra system permission. Basic history still works without it.";
"默认敏感应用会优先保护" = "Sensitive Apps Are Protected by Default";
"新安装时会默认把 Apple Passwords、Keychain Access、1Password 和 Bitwarden 加入应用例外；你也可以自行增删。" = "On a fresh install, Apple Passwords, Keychain Access, 1Password, and Bitwarden are added to app exceptions by default. You can adjust them yourself.";
"可能的网络访问" = "Possible Network Access";
"应用本身不做账号同步或后台上传；只有在剪贴板内容本身带有远程图片地址，且需要把它落成图片记录时，才可能访问对应地址。" = "The app does not sync accounts or upload in the background. It may access a URL only when the clipboard itself contains a remote image address and the app needs to turn it into an image record.";
"Edge Clip 在交互思路和体验打磨上，参考了多款优秀的开源项目。" = "Edge Clip draws interaction ideas and polish from several excellent open-source projects.";
"查看清单" = "View List";
"你可以在这里查看项目来源、对应仓库，以及它们帮助改进的使用体验。" = "You can review the project sources, their repositories, and the parts of the experience they helped improve here.";
"开源鸣谢" = "Open Source Credits";
"以下项目为 Edge Clip 提供了交互灵感或实现参考。点击 GitHub 可查看对应仓库。" = "The following projects provided interaction ideas or implementation references for Edge Clip. Click GitHub to view each repository.";
