"文本、图片和文件都能在同一个面板里快速找到。" = "Text, images, and files are easy to find in one panel.";
"先看再贴" = "Preview Before Pasting";
"支持搜索、预览和收藏，减少误贴和反复切换。" = "Search, preview, and favorites help reduce accidental pastes and repeated switching.";
"快速回贴" = "Quick Paste Back";
