"稍后再说" = "Later";
"现在去授权" = "Grant Permission Now";
"把刚刚复制过的内容，留在手边。" = "Keep What You Just Copied Within Reach.";
"Edge Clip 会把你最近复制过的文本、图片和文件整理进一个随手可开的侧边面板里，方便你继续查找、预览、收藏和回贴。" = "Edge Clip gathers your recently copied text, images, and files into a side panel that is always close at hand, making it easier to search, preview, favorite, and paste them back.";
"默认保留基础能力" = "Basic Features Stay Available";
"即使还没授予辅助功能权限，你也可以继续记录和查看基础历史。" = "Even without Accessibility permission, you can still record and view basic history.";
"敏感内容优先保护" = "Sensitive Content Comes First";
"会为常见密码管理器和敏感应用预置例外规则，你也可以自行调整。" = "Common password managers and sensitive apps are protected by default with exception rules, and you can adjust them yourself.";
"这份引导只会在首次启动时出现一次；后续你仍然可以在设置页查看隐私说明、权限状态和应用例外。" = "This guide appears only once on first launch. Later, you can still review privacy notes, permission status, and app exceptions in Settings.";
"边缘唤出" = "Edge Trigger";
"鼠标进入设定的屏幕边缘，面板会从左侧或右侧滑出。" = "Move the pointer to the configured screen edge and the panel slides out from the left or right.";
"快捷键唤出" = "Hotkey Trigger";
"支持双击修饰键或组合按键，适合键盘优先的工作流。" = "Supports double-modifier triggers and key combinations, which work well for keyboard-first workflows.";
"菜单栏入口" = "Menu Bar Entry";
"你可以从菜单栏图标打开面板、进入设置，或快速查看最近一条内容。" = "Open the panel, enter Settings, or glance at the latest item from the menu bar icon.";
"右键滑出" = "Right-Button Slide-Out";
"按住右键向外滑出可进入选择模式，适合不想频繁切手势的场景。" = "Hold the right mouse button and slide outward to enter selection mode. Great when you do not want to switch gestures often.";
"你不需要一次开启所有方式。建议先从自己最顺手的一种开始，再慢慢加。" = "You do not need to enable every method at once. Start with the one that feels most natural and add more later.";
"默认本地保存，边界明确。" = "Stored Locally by Default, With Clear Boundaries.";
"历史记录、收藏、资源文件和设置默认都保存在这台 Mac 上。详细声明里也会写清楚：哪些数据会落本地、哪些权限是可选的、什么情况下可能发生网络访问。" = "History, favorites, asset files, and settings are stored on this Mac by default. The full statement also explains what stays local, which permissions are optional, and when network access may happen.";
"本地历史与收藏" = "Local History and Favorites";
"文本、图片、文件记录与收藏内容默认只保存在本机目录。" = "Text, image, and file records, along with favorites, are stored only in local folders by default.";
"仅在剪贴板本身包含远程图片地址，且需要把它落成图片记录时，应用才可能访问该地址。" = "The app may access a remote image address only when the clipboard itself contains that address and it needs to turn it into an image record.";
"授权辅助功能可提升使用体验" = "Accessibility Permission Improves the Experience";
"授权后，Edge Clip 可以使用自动粘贴、全局唤出、右键滑出和部分预览快捷操作。如果暂时不授权，你依然可以继续使用基础历史记录与手动回贴。" = "Once permission is granted, Edge Clip can use auto paste, global triggers, right-button slide-out, and some preview shortcuts. If you skip it for now, you can still use basic history and paste manually.";
"会用到权限的能力：全局快捷键、右键滑出、恢复前台应用后自动发送 Cmd+V、部分预览态快捷键。" = "Features that use this permission: global hotkeys, right-button slide-out, automatically sending Cmd+V after returning to the front app, and some preview shortcuts.";
"不会因为你跳过授权而阻止进入应用。" = "Skipping permission will not block you from entering the app.";
"稍后你也可以随时在设置页重新触发授权。" = "You can trigger the permission flow again later from Settings at any time.";
"点击“现在去授权”后，我们会发起系统辅助功能授权请求，并同时打开对应的系统设置页面，方便你直接完成。" = "After you click \"Grant Permission Now,\" we will request Accessibility permission and open the matching System Settings page so you can complete it directly.";
